Ivanka Trump arrived in Israel yesterday for the opening of the US embassy in Jerusalem hours after the Israeli defence forces destroyed a tunnel near the main pedestrian crossing of the Gaza strip. Along with husband Jared Kushner, Ms Trump will lead the US delegation today to mark the decision to move US operations from Tel Aviv. 
